FT  11 JUL 94 / Mercury to seek review of BT fees
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
Mercury Communications is to lobby the government to review the fees it pays
British Telecommunications if BT's market share falls below 85 per cent.
BT has said the fees are needed to share the cost of upgrading the network.
